JNC 30 March 2025

Updated code with a slightly more detailed simulation for testing. A point source is inserted so that one can check in the image whether it appears in the correct location or not (see simulate_visibilities() in svsubs.c for more details). Seems to be working correctly.

Some details on the files in this commit are given below.

